   rdfs:comment """ClimOO developer comment:
We extend the domain and range of this object property to “system environment” as considerations regarding systems equally apply to system environments.This supports also representing hierarchies of sub/super-systems across systems and related environments. Consider, for instance, cases when certain systems of interest are components of the system environments of other systems of interest, or when the system environment of a system of interest is another or part of another system interest."""@en
 ] .

[ rdf:type owl:Axiom ;
   owl:annotatedSource :ClimOO_0000077 ;
   owl:annotatedProperty rdfs:range ;
   owl:annotatedTarget _:genid13 ;
   rdfs:comment """ClimOO developer comment:
We extend the domain and range of this object property to “system environment” as considerations regarding systems equally apply to system environments.This supports also representing hierarchies of sub/super-systems across systems and related environments. Consider, for instance, cases when certain systems of interest are components of the system environments of other systems of interest, or when the system environment of a system of interest is another or part of another system interest."""@en
