###  http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_01000741
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_01000741> rdfs:subClassOf <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_03000043> ,
                                                               [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
