###  http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_01000993
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_01000993> rdfs:comment """ClimOO Ontology developer comment:
Concerning plastic-related subclasses: we focused on production and manufacturing processes related to synthetic plastic polymers, materials, and objects. More general references to synthetic polymers, related materials, and objects can be added as needed.

We primarily focused on biodegradability in relation to synthetic plastics, related polymers and items. Reference to biodegradability concerning plastics more in general, for instance in relation to natural plastics, or in relation to polymer-based materials can be added as needed."""@en ,
                                                            """ClimOO Ontology revised definition:
Reference to supply chains and related activities may be added, as neeed. Subclasses may be specified.""" .


