###  http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_02500036
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_02500036> rdfs:subClassOf <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000015> ;
                                               rdfs:comment """ClimOO Ontology developer comment:
Given the EnvO axiomatization of this class, we intend the “environment” term in the definition to refer to environmental materials. 

We reclassified this class as a subclass of BFO “process” instead of “environmental process” to comply with revisions ensuring SCO-EnvO alignment. We also extend the axiomatization of this class to include reference to environmental systems (and related environments).
We envision further discussions with subject matter experts to implement the CimOO Ontology representation of pollution, for instance concerning whether pollution processe are (always/only) tranportation processes (EnvO sensus)."""@en ;
                                               <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> """ClimOO Ontology revised definition:
A process that results in the introduction of contaminants into an environmental material (environmental system or related environment)."""@en .


###  http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_02500040
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_02500040> rdfs:subClassOf [ owl:intersectionOf ( [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                        owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000057> ;
                                                                                        owl:someValuesFrom :ClimOO_0000164
                                                                                      ]
                                                                                      [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                        owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000057> ;
                                                                                        owl:someValuesFrom :ClimOO_0000166
                                                                                      ]
                                                                                      [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                        owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002234> ;
                                                                                        owl:someValuesFrom [ owl:intersectionOf ( :ClimOO_0000164
                                                                                                                                  [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                                    owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_02000200> ;
                                                                                                                                    owl:someValuesFrom :ClimOO_0000163
                                                                                                                                  ]
                                                                                                                                ) ;
                                                                                                             rdf:type owl:Class
                                                                                                           ]
                                                                                      ]
                                                                                      [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                        owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002234> ;
                                                                                        owl:someValuesFrom [ owl:intersectionOf ( :ClimOO_0000166
                                                                                                                                  [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                                    owl:onProperty [ owl:inverseOf <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_02000200>
                                                                                                                                                   ] ;
                                                                                                                                    owl:someValuesFrom :ClimOO_0000163
                                                                                                                                  ]
                                                                                                                                ) ;
                                                                                                             rdf:type owl:Class
                                                                                                           ]
                                                                                      ]
                                                                                    ) ;
                                                                 rdf:type owl:Class
                                                               ] ;
                                               rdfs:comment """ClimOO Ontology developer comment:
EnvO refers plastic pollution to the presence of some plastic material in the environment. However, the pollutant is not simply the material itself, but the object/piece/item made of such material. Also, with the term “plastic pollution”, we usually do not just refer to pollution of plastic items (material science sense) but more generally to also that caused by items, more generally, made of polymer-based materials. Thus, we revise the definition and the axiomatization of this class."""@en ,
                                                            """ClimOO Ontology developer:
Implementations will expand current representation to distinguish intentional from unintentional plastic pollution processes."""@en ;
                                               <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> """ClimOO Ontology revised definition:
A pollution process during which plastic debris particles are released and accumulated into an environmental material, from some plastic debris source to some plastic debris sink."""@en ;
                                               <https://www.w3id.org/sco#SCO_0000039> :ClimOO_0000072 ,
                                                                                      :ClimOO_0000073 ,
                                                                                      :ClimOO_0000074 ,
                                                                                      :ClimOO_0000075 ,
                                                                                      :ClimOO_0000228 .

[ rdf:type owl:Axiom ;
   owl:annotatedSource <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_02500040> ;
   owl:annotatedProperty rdfs:comment ;
   owl:annotatedTarget """ClimOO Ontology developer comment:
EnvO refers plastic pollution to the presence of some plastic material in the environment. However, the pollutant is not simply the material itself, but the object/piece/item made of such material. Also, with the term “plastic pollution”, we usually do not just refer to pollution of plastic items (material science sense) but more generally to also that caused by items, more generally, made of polymer-based materials. Thus, we revise the definition and the axiomatization of this class."""@en ;
   <https://www.w3id.org/sco#SCO_0000039> :ClimOO_0000072
 ] .


