###  http://purl.unep.org/sdg/SDGIO_00000013
<http://purl.unep.org/sdg/SDGIO_00000013> rdfs:subClassOf [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                            owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000176> ;
                                                            owl:someValuesFrom <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_01000254>
                                                          ] ;
                                          rdfs:comment """ClimOO developer comment:
For ClimOO Ontology purposes, we restrict this class to refer specifically to environmental systems. Similarly, we also constrain that a resource to be always part of a environmental system of interest. This class can be generalized to all systems and possibly system environments, as needed."""@en ,
                                                       """ClimOO developer comment:
Further wok is required to represent the relation between system resources and system components."""@en .


