[ rdf:type owl:Axiom ;
   owl:annotatedSource :ClimOO_0000096 ;
   owl:annotatedProperty <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> ;
   owl:annotatedTarget "a piece of polymer-based synthetic material (no packaging) that is part of and used in an agricultural ecosystem."@en ;
   <http://purl.org/dc/terms/source> "https://environment.ec.europa.eu/system/files/2021-09/Agricultural%20Plastics%20Final%20Report.pdf" ;
   rdfs:comment """According to FAO (2021), agriplastics also count for plastic items used in aquaculture. We currently exclude reference to such objects as the ClimOO Ontology is on crop cultivation. 

FAO. 2021. Assessment of agricultural plastics and their sustainability. A call for action. Rome. https://doi.org/10.4060/cb7856enThe"""
 ] .


