                                                       ]
                                                     ) ;
                                  rdf:type owl:Class
                                ] ;
                <http://purl.org/dc/terms/source> """Compendium of polymer terminology and nomenclature: IUPAC recommendations, 2008. (2009). Choice (Middletown), 47(01), 47-0284-47–0284.

Vert, M., Doi, Y., Hellwich, K.-H., Hess, M., Hodge, P., Kubisa, P., Rinaudo, M., & Schué, F. (2012). Terminology for biorelated polymers and applications (IUPAC Recommendations 2012). Pure Appl. Chem., 84(2), 377–410."""@en ;
