                                                         owl:someValuesFrom :ClimOO_0000141
                                                       ]
                                                     ) ;
                                  rdf:type owl:Class
                                ] ;
                <http://purl.org/dc/terms/source> """Compendium of polymer terminology and nomenclature: IUPAC recommendations, 2008. (2009). Choice (Middletown), 47(01), 47-0284-47–0284.

Vert, M., Doi, Y., Hellwich, K.-H., Hess, M., Hodge, P., Kubisa, P., Rinaudo, M., & Schué, F. (2012). Terminology for biorelated polymers and applications (IUPAC Recommendations 2012). Pure Appl. Chem., 84(2), 377–410."""@en ;
                rdfs:label "polymerization process"@en ;
                rdfs:seeAlso "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0302890; http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCIT_C34072; http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REX_0000251; http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/MOP_0000629." ;
                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A process that converts some input monomers (at least two) into some polymer."@en ;
                <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Released> .


