[ rdf:type owl:Axiom ;
   owl:annotatedSource :ClimOO_0000202 ;
   owl:annotatedProperty rdfs:subClassOf ;
   owl:annotatedTarget _:genid1666 ;
   rdfs:comment "This axiom requires revisions. Implementations are needed to further restrict the class coverage to cases of interest. Currently the model allows some undesirable cases, such as when pollutants released and acquired are not the same."@en ,
                "We envision implementing this representation by including references to specific sources and sinks. Correspondences with plastic debris sources/sinks can be clarified as well."@en ,
                """ClimOO Ontology developer comment:
Implementations may revise this axiom with reference to more adequate and specific object properties to represent variations of levels of plastic debris presence. Revisions will primarily target the object property “increased levels of”.
Also, see comments to the object property “increased levels of”.

http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_02000200""" ;
   <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Provisional>
 ] .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo#ClimOO_0000203
:ClimOO_0000203 rdf:type owl:Class ;
                rdfs:subClassOf <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_23367> ,
                                [ owl:intersectionOf ( <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000030>
                                                       [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                         owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000176> ;
                                                         owl:someValuesFrom <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_06105112>
                                                       ]
                                                       [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                         owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0000087> ;
                                                         owl:someValuesFrom [ rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                                              owl:unionOf ( <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_01000665>
                                                                                            :ClimOO_0000206
                                                                                          )
                                                                            ]
                                                       ]
                                                       [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                         owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002353> ;
                                                         owl:someValuesFrom <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_06105125>
                                                       ]
                                                     ) ;
                                  rdf:type owl:Class
                                ] ;
                rdfs:comment "An upper-level class concerning residues included in polymer materials other than plastics can be added as needed."@en ,
                             "Here the focus is on the actual molecules that are residual molecules incorporated into the plastic materials. If the need arises for a more meso- or macroscopical representation of residues, the ClimOO Ontology will implement the current model."@en ,
                             "References to molecule that are accidentally incorporated but are not an output of the manufacturing process can be added if needed."@en ;
                rdfs:label "residue molecule of synthetic plastic manufacturing"@en ;
                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A molecule that is a waste or byproduct of some plastic manufacturing process (is an output and bearer some waste or byproduct role) and is incorporated into some synthetic plastic material."@en ;
                <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Released> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo#ClimOO_0000204
