###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo#ClimOO_0000206
:ClimOO_0000206 rdf:type owl:Class ;
                rdfs:comment """This class aims to be a generalization of the SuMSO \"by-product-role\" class, as for the \"waste-role\" and \"product-role\" classes. For a definition, see the SuMSO class, without considering references to supply chains.

See also:
https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000159
http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_01000665
https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000160
https://www.w3id.org/climoo#ClimOO_0000235
https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000053"""@en ;
                rdfs:label "by-product role"@en .


